blogs.title: Squirrel in my house
blogs.content: Last night a squirrel came into my house. I'm nervous.
blogs.author: david

blogs.title: It has not gone
blogs.content: When I woke, the squirrel was still there.
blogs.author: david

blogs.title: Staring at me
blogs.content: I entered the room to usher it out, but it just stared at me.
blogs.author: david

blogs.title: We are friends
blogs.content: After much staring, I have befriended the squirrel.
blogs.author: david

blogs.title: Where has it gone
blogs.content: The squirrel has left my house
blogs.author: david
